overview.en: Tree is the world's first blockchain-based yew property token, and each Tree is 100% anchored to the real growing Mandianian yew.Holding Tree can enjoy the asset appreciation brought by the natural growth of Yew;At the same time, the holder of
means the owner of the corresponding property right of taxus chinensis, and the corresponding taxus chinensis can be taken from the Tree ecological base.
overview.zh: Tree是世界上第一个基于区块链的红豆杉地产代币，每棵树都100%锚定在真正生长的曼地亚红豆杉上。持有Tree可以享受红豆杉自然生长带来的资产增值；同时，“树木”的持有人是指红豆杉相应产权的所有者，相应的红豆杉可以从树木生态基础中提取。
